             was indicted for <rs id="t17941111-44-off213" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17941111-44-off213" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17941111-44-off213" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bigamy"></interp>
               that he, on the 16th of May 1771 in the town of Baldock, in the county of Hertfordshire, did marry 
                     <persName id="t17941111-44-victim584" type="victimName">
                        Sarah 
                        Marshall
                     <interp inst="t17941111-44-victim584" type="surname" value="Marshall"></interp>
