                        <interp inst="t17941111-44-victim584" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , spinster; and that he also, on the <rs id="t17941111-44-cd214" type="crimeDate">30th of May, and in the thirtieth year of his present Majesty's reign</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17941111-44-off213 t17941111-44-cd214"></join>, did marry and take to wife, Margery 
                     
                        <persName id="t17941111-44-victim586" type="victimName">
                           Sophia 
                           Richardson
                        <interp inst="t17941111-44-victim586" type="surname" value="Richardson"></interp>
